==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Chamisal
<hw>Cha`mi*sal"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Amer. Sp.,
fr. Sp. <ets>chamiza</ets> a kind of wild cane.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A California rosaceous shrub (<spn>Adenostoma
fasciculatum</spn>) which often forms an impenetrable
chaparral.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A chaparral formed by dense growths of this
shrub.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chamlet</ent>⟦br⟧
